cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM. 

The paper deals with automated nuclear segmentation in histology images, which is a problem in computer vision and image analysis. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a novel convolutional neural network, which falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The evaluation framework proposed in the paper involves comparing the performance of different segmentation methods, which is a task in information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
